title: Krystyna Hutchinson Answers Your Questions!
description:
Kippy and Foley are joined by returning guest and old pal Krystyna Hutchinson. We answer your questions and talk trashy tattoos, fighting with family, drag racing, and whole bunch more. Its a fun one!


Bonus episodes: https://www.patreon.com/AreYouGarbage?fan_landing=true
